text: Moon Girl and Devil Dinosaurio is an Moon Girls and el Dinosaurio animated television series. It was developed by Steve Loter, Jeffrey M. Howard, and Kate Kondell for Disney Channel. It is based on the characters of the same names by Marvel Comics. The series follows Lunella Lafayette and her dinosaur companion "Devil Dinosaur". It stars the voices of Diamond White, Fred Tatasciore, Alfre Woodard, Sasheer Zamata, Jermaine Fowler, Gary Anthony Williams, Libe Barer, and Laurence Fishburne. The series premiered on February 10, 2023. Category:2020s American animated television series Category:2023 American television series debuts Category:Television series by Disney
